Package: libdleyna-server-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libdleyna-server-1.0-1 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: APIs for DMS discovery and browsing - development files
 dLeyna-server provides APIs for discovering Digital Media Servers
 and for browsing and searching their contents. dLeyna-server can
 be used in conjunction with a multimedia framework, such as
 GStreamer, to implement a Digital Media Player. It can also be
 used to implement the DLNA Download System Use Case.
 .
 This package contains the header files for the library and other
 development files.

Package: libdleyna-server-1.0-1
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: APIs for DMS discovery and browsing
 dLeyna-server provides APIs for discovering Digital Media Servers
 and for browsing and searching their contents. dLeyna-server can
 be used in conjunction with a multimedia framework, such as
 GStreamer, to implement a Digital Media Player. It can also be
 used to implement the DLNA Download System Use Case.
